qa_pairs.question: Who is the principal of APS Mangla?
qa_pairs.answer: Talat Wazir is the principal of APS Mangla

qa_pairs.question: What subjects are taught in ICS?
qa_pairs.answer: ICS subjects include Physics, Maths, Computer, English, Urdu and Islamiyat for 1st year. For 2nd year, Pak Studies replaces Islamiyat
